From f13cc803dc0cb68d3f32fa21f4ce74d865df3863 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:05:33 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] ADD review completion prompts for closing finished patch
 chats

Clean reviews now ask the patch-agent chat whether the feature is done so users can close completed work from the same conversation. Yes/y records the chat as done without contacting the backend, while no or later typing records the feature as reopened before work continues.
